  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    org.threadly.concurrent.CentralThreadlyPool.lowPriorityPool(boolean)
    use CentralThreadlyPool.lowPrioritySingleThreadPool() or CentralThreadlyPool.lowPriorityPool()
    org.threadly.concurrent.CentralThreadlyPool.lowPriorityPool(boolean, String)
    use CentralThreadlyPool.lowPrioritySingleThreadPool(String) or CentralThreadlyPool.lowPriorityPool(String)

    Please use ControlledThreadProfiler.removeProfiledThread(Thread)

    Please use SameThreadSubmitterExecutor.instance().execute(r) as an alternative
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.FutureUtils.scheduleWhileTaskResultNull(SubmitterScheduler, long, boolean, Callable<? extends T>)
    Please use FutureUtils.scheduleWhile(SubmitterScheduler, long, boolean, Callable, Predicate)
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.FutureUtils.scheduleWhileTaskResultNull(SubmitterScheduler, long, boolean, Callable<? extends T>, long)
    Please use with a simple null checking Predicate FutureUtils.scheduleWhile(SubmitterScheduler, long, boolean, Callable, Predicate, long, boolean)
